{"tid":2411334,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人類的疾病觀","createTime":"2021-02-17T08:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T07:26:27.000Z","uid":47901,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bd918c22295caef5c9394da90722b5bb29e0e3be","tid":2411334,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:59:37.000Z","msg":"在世上有好多種貓科動物<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n某人類族群認為山獅是&ldquo;正常&rdquo;的貓科動物<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kw3uHrZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkw3uHrZ.jpg&h=2ac0238c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iyZ9Hsy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiyZ9Hsy.jpg&h=386347d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他們有時見到一d好大的或好細的貓科動物，會覺得佢地好唔正常，例如東北虎或者普通的家貓，會好質疑這些異常體形的貓科動物如何謀生<br />\n<br />\n因此，這人類族群常常想辦法去&ldquo;矯正&rdquo;其他有別於山獅的貓科動物：&ldquo;這些家貓的體形太細了，難以捕捉野豬，這些老虎的體形太龐大了，難以在山石叢林中跳躍穿插&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n所以這人類族群用了極大的精神時間勞力去 &ldquo;矯正，治療&rdquo; 他們眼中那些 &quot;異常&quot; 的貓科動物，而花費了那麼多時間心力勞力，這人類族群的糧倉，農田等卻被大量的老鼠侵入並把糧食吃盡，有一些連山獅都敵不過的大形動物也闖入並毀壞那人類族群的家園"},{"pid":"e5096f2b3ac2df9a6fdc98d1975be112148076ce","tid":2411334,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T09:09:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UubvR2NTKLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUubvR2NTKLA&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2zMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=d139519f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UubvR2NTKLA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/X6Uidi2mD84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FX6Uidi2mD84&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2zMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=d3f62396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/X6Uidi2mD84</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EAc7xps9lHo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEAc7xps9lHo&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2zMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=2f69fc78\" data-auto-link ta